<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Montgomery </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The Montgomery Community Association administers the area and operates a hockey rink and an outdoor skating rink. The association also hosts bingo and sports programs.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community hall has wheelchair access, a gym, commercial kitchen, stage and meeting room.Also available is the Shouldice Aquatic Centre, with a pool and dive tank.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">In the southwest portion of the community is the Shouldice Arena and Athletic Park, complete with a hockey rink, four soccer fields, a baseball field, seven softball fields and three football fields, all available for bookings March through November.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">To the West lies and to the north, in , is Market Mall, one of Calgaryâ€™s largest indoor shopping malls, with over 200 stores, including The Bay, Old Navy and Apple Store (the first one to open in Calgary). Built in a racetrack style layout, the mall is easy to navigate. Food is easy to find in the mall as well, with a standard food court, as well as a Moxie's Classic Grill and a Milestones.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Montgomery has an elementary school and a junior high school operated by the CBE.</p>
        </div>
